4374">奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 在摇滚名人堂入职演讲中所说的话</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Ozzy-Osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本</a>昨晚入选摇滚名人堂。看看他在下面的就职演讲中所说的话。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ozzy-osbourne-tour-retirement-black-sabbath-3390656">奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）：无与伦比的摇滚表演者</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位黑暗王子曾于 2006 年成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑色安息日</a>乐队的成员，昨晚（10 月 19 日）以独唱艺术家的身份回归，接受了这一荣誉——这是他自 2006 年以来一直有资格获得的荣誉。</p><p>在俄亥俄州克利夫兰的 Rocket Mortgage FieldHouse 举行的颁奖典礼上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Billy-Idol">Billy Idol</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Tool">Tool 乐队</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maynard-james-keenan">Maynard James Keenan</a>和乡村艺术家 Jelly Roll 以及由贝斯手 Rob Trujillo 组成的伴奏乐队向这位歌手的独唱生涯致敬。在加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Metallica">Metallica</a>之前，奥斯本乐队成员包括 Zakk Wylde、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Wolfgang-Van-Halen">Wolfgang Van Halen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Red-Hot-Chili-Peppers">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a>的 Chad Smith、吉他手 Steve Stevens 和制作人 Andrew Watt。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-black-to-induct-ozzy-osbourne-into-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-3799511">随后，杰克·布莱克（Jack Black）向他介绍了他</a>，他告诉观众：“当然，你可以去观看<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/post-malone">波兹·马龙</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>的节目，并获得你破碎的心所需的所有温暖拥抱。或者，您也可以彻夜不眠，第一次被 Ozzy 的整个目录所震惊。天啊！你们这些孩子真他妈的幸运。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBVPjXBsIw8/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 